dct_description_sm: Shows county boundaries and township grid. Includes railroad lines.; Indexes of railroad stations and electric lines included under map title.; Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington, D.C.; Inset maps: North-western portion of Florida -- Dry Tortugas.; On verso: Index to counties and towns with 1900 population.; In pencil on verso of University Libraries' copy: "About 1915."
56 x 40 Centimeters, on sheet 59 x 54 Centimeters
